<TEXT>
<P>
GUANGZHOU, December 6 (Xinhua) -- The '97 International Art
Fair started today in Guangzhou, the capital of south China's
Guangdong province.
</P>
<P>
The purpose of the fair, which has 400 booths for approximately
10,000 works of art from more than 10 countries and regions,
