<HEADLINE> Five Killed in Tanzania Road Accident </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DAR ES SALAAM, December 6 (Xinhua) -- Five people died on the
spot Friday and three others injured in a road accident in Mtwara
Urban District, northern Tanzania, The Guardian paper reported
today.
</P>
<P>
The accident occurred at Kabisera near Mikindani town when an
eight-ton lorry travelling from Mtwara to Masasi collided with a
10-ton lorry which was carrying bags of cashew-nuts, police said.
