<HEADLINE> Fireworks Warehouse Blast Kills 12 40 in Ecuador </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Quito, December 5 (Xinhua) -- An explosion rocked the
commercial center in Guayaquil, the biggest industrial city of
Ecuador today, killing at least 12 persons and injured 40 others.
</P>
<P>
The blast took place at 8:00 local time at a warehouse full of
fireworks to be used for the new year festivities. 
</P>
</TEXT>
