Louise, Canada, on Friday.
</P>
<P>
Seizinger clocked a combined time of one minute 38.86 seconds
for the win, followed by Melanie Suchet of France in the second
place in 1:39.05.
</P>
<P>
Isolde Kostner of Italy claimed the third place with a time of
1:39.38. 
